                    <ab>In n(omine) D[omini. Constat me <persName key="#Abbots"><name
                                ref="Richardus">Rich]ardus</name></persName> gr(aci)a D(e)i <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abb(as)</rs> reg(u)l(e) <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >mon(a)sterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1487">S(an)c(t)i
                            Apollinarii q(ui) voc(atur) No[vo</orgName> a]ccepiss[em et] accepi a
                        vob(is) <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                            >Deusdedit</name></persName> gr(aci)a D(e)i <rs key="#Priests"
                            >p(res)b(ite)r</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1471">s(an)c(t)e <placeName
                                ref="#places/594">R[avennatis</placeName>] Eccl(esi)e</orgName>
                        [pensionem] [pro <rs key="#Landed_possessions">t]rib(us) [unciis] in
                            in(te)g(ro</rs>) q(ue) sunt posit[e] in [<rs key="#Fundi">fu]ndo</rs>
                        q(ui) v[ocatur <geogName key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money"
                            ref="#estates/2421"><placeName
                                key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Rent_in_money"
                                >C]olopedio</placeName></geogName> cu(m) om(n)ib(us) sibi
                        [pertinentibus, <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>] <geogName key="#Fines"
                            ref="#estates/2422"><placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/3515"
                                >Liviense</placeName></geogName>, <rs key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1488">S(an)c(t)e
                            Reparate</orgName>, quas p(er) <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >enfiteo[sin</rs> tenere] [visi estis ad iura suprascripti monasterii
                        nostri, et per unaquaque indicione <rs key="#Rent_in_money">denarii
                            quinque</rs> tantum. Unde] p(ro) munimine v(est)ro feci vob(is) h[oc
                        de]accepto in m(en)se m(arcio), indic[ione ..., Ravenne]. [Richardus
                        presbiter] et mon(achus) atq(ue) abb(as) reg(u)l(e) S(an)c(t)i Apoll(inaris)
                        q(ui) v(ocatur) Novo in hoc diaccepto manus meas s(ub)s(cripsi). Eg[o ...]
                        [...]. [In nomine Domini. Eg]o Richard(us) p(res)b(ite)[r] et mon(achus)
                        atq(ue) abb(as) reg(u)l(e) mon(a)s(terii) S(an)c(t)i Apoll(inaris) q(ui)
                        v(ocatur) Novo in hoc diacc[epto] mano mea s(ub)s(cripsi) p(er) ind(icione)
                        [...].</ab>
